comment.en: Chosen major for general high school seniors. Can be either of the following options: a broad subject area (economics, literature or sciences), or a combination of two high school specialty among thirteen possibilities
Includes university curricula leading to long-term studies
Student in last year of high school
Higher education schools that are not part of university. Mainly includes private institutions
Can be linked to student and seen as a center of interest. Can be linked to university curricula and high school majors and be seen as a descriptive feature
Includes university curricula leading to short-term studies
University curriculum a student is following or has followed recently
Curriculum mentioned by a student as an alternative or as a possible choice for future studies
